EN: Institutions at all levels should actively promote child education.

ZH: 各级职工都应该遵守劳动纪律。
EN: Workers at all levels should abide by labor discipline.

ZH: 各级领导干部应该密切关注人民群众的需求。
EN: Leaders and cadres at all levels should pay close attention to the needs of the people.

ZH: 各级部门都应该加强协作，共同解决问题。
EN: Departments at all levels should strengthen cooperation and jointly solve problems.

ZH: 各级医院应该提供优质的医疗服务。
EN: Hospitals at all levels should provide high-quality medical services.

ZH: 各级学员都要积极参与社会实践。
EN: Trainees at all levels should actively participate in social practice.

ZH: 各级法院都要公正审判，保障司法公正。
EN: Courts at all levels should conduct fair trials to guarantee judicial justice.

